model.network

Class NetworkHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.network.NetworkHandler

  • public class NetworkHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that looks after what kind of Updates have occured in another Player's game world and delegates to each of the types of interactions then calls interact on them on this Client/Server
